Racket [01-05 of 05] (1992) TVRip

"Racket" ("... through intimidation, violence and blackmail") - of a five-series Russian television film, a crime thriller studio TO "screen", filmed in 1992 by Ernest Yasan scenario written in collaboration with Victor Merezhko. Work on the film began in 1989 and was originally planned to stay in the 15-series film. The prototype for the protagonist has become identity Petersburg television journalist Alexander Nevzorov

Director: Ernest Yasan
Cast: Vladimir Eremin, Sergey Shkalikov, Natalia Danilova, Anna Samokhina, Irina Klimova, Alexander Demyanenko, V. Yumatov, Vanya Merezhko
===========================
The television program "Radar" , as well as leading and Alex Kornilov, due to its controversial content dedicated to the criminal side of city life, incredibly popular with viewers. Besides activities Kornilov displeases local mafia after he interviews Gridasova , one of the bosses of the underworld.

Gridasova the next day is found dead . Kornilov secretly videotaped his funeral , attended by criminals of all kinds. Videotape with filming the funeral and the journalist becomes the object of this hunt by criminals .

Meanwhile, the trail goes mafia police captain Dmitry Glazkov , who learned about supplying large quantities of drugs in the coffins of the dead soldiers. Ways Glazkova Kornilov intersect ...
